850
01:02:20,407 --> 01:02:21,396
[CELL PHONE RINGING]

851
01:02:29,207 --> 01:02:31,767
We'll be in touch, Bobby.

852
01:02:31,927 --> 01:02:33,201
Hello?

853
01:02:36,207 --> 01:02:37,799
It's done.

854
01:02:37,967 --> 01:02:40,162
Vel, is the money there?

855
01:02:41,167 --> 01:02:42,441
Okay, good.

856
01:02:42,607 --> 01:02:46,043
I've done everything you want.
When do I get my family back?

857
01:02:46,207 --> 01:02:49,165
We have some tidying up to do.

858
01:03:06,167 --> 01:03:10,160
Sir, I just wanted to say, regardless
