These are archive files.

863
01:03:24,687 --> 01:03:26,518
MAN: Ninety-one cameras
running on 20 screens.

864
01:03:26,847 --> 01:03:29,281
Wow, I bet you don't watch much TV
when you get home.

865
01:03:29,447 --> 01:03:31,119
I don't even have one.

866
01:03:31,327 --> 01:03:32,316
[GLASS SHATTERING]

867
01:03:32,487 --> 01:03:33,681
- Sorry. Sorry.
- I got it.

868
01:03:54,247 --> 01:03:55,805
Okay.

869
01:03:57,127 --> 01:03:59,197
Well, at least it didn't end up
in the keyboard.

870
01:03:59,367 --> 01:04:00,402
MAN:
Right.

871
01:04:02,767 --> 01:04:06,123
We better get out of here before
we completely screw things up.

872
01:04:06,287 --> 01:04:07,879
- Thanks. Sorry.
- Thank you.

873
01:04:08,047 --> 01:04:09,844
All right.

874
01:04:19,727 --> 01:04:21,877
- Where's Jack Stanfield?
- He just left.

875
01:04:22,047 --> 01:04:24,766
- What was he doing in here?
- Making one hell of a mess.

876
01:04:24,927 --> 01:04:27,805
- What the hell?
- What's wrong?

877
01:04:29,527 --> 01:04:31,279
MAN:
All the camera files have been deleted.

878
01:04:44,887 --> 01:04:46,525
JACK: What is this?
COX: Just press "send."

879
01:04:57,247 --> 01:05:00,205
