883
01:05:15,447 --> 01:05:17,563
See you at the house, Jack.

884
01:05:21,967 --> 01:05:25,084
Jack, what's going on?
What are you up to?

885
01:05:25,247 --> 01:05:27,807
- I haven't got time for this now.
- You're gonna make time.

886
01:05:27,967 --> 01:05:31,926
