were doing in areas you shouldn't be in.

887
01:05:32,087 --> 01:05:33,964
No, I'm not.

888
01:05:34,767 --> 01:05:37,361
- Mr. Stanfield, the network...
- Tell him.

889
01:05:37,527 --> 01:05:40,200
- What is it?
- The network just crashed.

890
01:05:40,367 --> 01:05:42,198
- The whole floor?
- No, the whole building.

891
01:05:42,447 --> 01:05:44,119
[TIRES SCREECHING]

892
01:05:50,127 --> 01:05:51,685
Stanfield!

893
01:05:57,927 --> 01:05:59,440
Jack! Stop right there!

894
01:05:59,607 --> 01:06:01,199
Jack!

895
01:06:08,767 --> 01:06:10,405
- Get out of the car!
- Are you nuts?

896
01:06:10,567 --> 01:06:12,000
GARY: You're nuts!
- Get away.

897
01:06:12,167 --> 01:06:16,206
Security-camera files are missing,
the computers just crashed...!

898
01:06:29,607 --> 01:06:30,881
Call the police.

899
01:06:31,047 --> 01:06:33,686
Security. We're in the garage,
get the police.

900
01:06:33,847 --> 01:06:34,836
Shit.

901
01:06:50,807 --> 01:06:52,718
JACK:
Beth?

902
01:06:55,527 --> 01:06:57,199
Beth!

903
01:07:03,087 --> 01:07:04,884
Beth!

904
01:07:07,967 --> 01:07:09,639
Beth?

905
01:07:12,327 --> 01:07:13,999
Oh, my God.

906
01:07:48,407 --> 01:07:49,726
[PHONE RINGING]

907
01:07:53,207 --> 01:07:55,516
